Adds an axe, pick, shovel and sword at high strength and speed made from the "blazing" block.

Crafting

* A blazing block can be crafted from four lumps of coal, four gold
  ingots and one bucket of lava. Empty buckets are returned upon crafting.
  Blazing blocks emit light.

* Blazing tools can be crafted using the same standard recipes used by other
  tools, substituting blazing blocks for the tool heads.

Mod Compatibility

* Blazing tools emit light if the wielded_light mod is also installed.
* Blazing tools can be enchanted if the x_enchanting mod is also installed.
